                <p>Will let CIFM know [probably about John Murray’s terms for an Italian translation of <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>].</p>
                <p>Thanks for information about hornless fossil <hi rend="italic">Bos etruscus</hi> and Miocene fossils of genus <hi rend="italic">Sus</hi> [see <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>, 2d ed., pp. 505, 521].</p>
